Compiler command - for creating assembly file
gcc -S -o hello_world.s hello_world.c

assembler command
as -o hello_world.o hello_world.s

linker command
ld -o hello_world -lc -dynamic-linker /lib/ld-linux.so.2 hello_world.o -e main

for 64 bit - linux library is /lib64/ld-linux-x86-64.so.2


https://www.cprogramming.com/tutorial/shared-libraries-linux-gcc.html